---
title: Rustic Italian Stew with Bacon and Cheesy Croutons
description: Mamma mia! We’re excited to bring you this deliciously hearty and rustic stew. It’s got all the good stuff: homemade Parmesan croutons, crispy bacon, rich tomato base - mmm we couldn't ask for anything more!
